{% doc %}
  @prompt
    
    Design a premium two-column hero section with strong visual hierarchy, bold typography, product-focused branding, and an integrated lifestyle image slider.
    
    Layout Requirements
    
    * Full-width hero section
    * Optional background image with fallback background color
    * Two-column layout (50% / 50%) on desktop
    * On mobile: slider appears first, content appears below
    * Proper spacing and alignment across all breakpoints
    
    
    Left Column – Content Area
    
    Include the following fully customizable settings:
    
    1. Small badge text (editable text field)
    2. Product image upload (support 2–3 images displayed in a slightly overlapped layered layout)
    3. Main heading (rich text with HTML support + optional “All Caps” toggle)
    4. Short description (rich text field)
    5. Two CTA buttons:
    
       * Primary button (solid style, customizable label + URL)
       * Secondary button (outline style, customizable label + URL)
    6. Small supporting rich text below buttons (e.g., trust indicators like “Veteran Owned • Zero Sugar”)
    
    
    
    Styling Controls (via schema):
    
    * Dark overlay enable/disable
    * Overlay opacity range slider (0–100)
    * Text alignment (left / center)
    * Button color customization
    * Section padding (top & bottom)
    * Mobile spacing control
    
    Design must ensure:
    
    * Strong contrast (white/light text on dark background)
    * Modern typography
    * Smooth hover animations on buttons
    * Clean, premium layout
    
     Right Column – Lifestyle Image Slider
    
    Create a lightweight, performance-optimized image slider using native JavaScript (no jQuery or heavy libraries).
    
    ### Slider Features:
    
    * Image blocks (dynamic blocks with image picker)
    * Autoplay enable/disable toggle
    * Autoplay speed control (milliseconds)
    * Transition style option (fade or slide)
    * Pause on hover option
    * Navigation dots at bottom
    * Lazy loading enabled
    * Accessible controls (aria attributes)
    
    Ensure smooth transitions and minimal JS footprint.
    
    ---
    
    ## 🔹 Bottom Decorative Divider
    
    Add an optional bottom divider element:
    
    * Image upload option (wave / torn-edge style)
    * Adjustable height control
    * Overlap effect with next section
    * Enable/disable toggle
    
    Divider should visually layer over the next section for a modern design effect.
    
    ---
    
    🔹 Schema Requirements
    
    Implement a complete Shopify 2.0 schema including:
    
    * Background image picker
    * Background color fallback
    * Overlay opacity control
    * Padding controls
    * Alignment controls
    * Button customization settings
    * Slider autoplay toggle
    * Divider image upload
    * Image slider blocks
    * Preset configuration included
    
    Use proper:
    
    * `{% schema %}`
    * `{% endschema %}`
    * Blocks for slider images
    * Presets array
    
    Technical Standards
    
    * Clean, semantic HTML
    * Scoped CSS within the section
    * Flexbox or CSS Grid layout
    * Fully responsive
    * Accessible markup (ARIA where required)
    * Performance optimized
    * No jQuery
    * No external heavy dependencies
    * Production-ready and maintainable code
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-premium-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__background-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__background-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px 40px {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    {% else %}
      align-items: flex-start;
      text-align: left;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.badge_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-images-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}center{% else %}flex-start{% endif %};
    height: 200px;
    margin: 10px 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(1) {
    z-index: 3;
    left: 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) {
    z-index: 2;
    left: 120px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) {
    z-index: 1;
    left: 240px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
    {% if block.settings.heading_all_caps %}
      text-transform: uppercase;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_text }};
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover_bg }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_text }};
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.secondary_button_border }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover_bg }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover_border }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__support-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.support_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.support_text_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 600px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slider-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    opacity: 1;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slide-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__slide-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    max-height: 400px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    width: 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: {{ block.settings.divider_height }}px;
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-premium-hero__divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-premium-hero__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      order: -1;
      height: 400px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px 24px {{ block.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__product-images-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: 140px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) {
      left: 90px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) {
      left: 180px;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-premium-hero__button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-premium-hero__button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 140px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<premium-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-premium-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-premium-hero__background-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.background_image %}
      <img
        src="{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}"
        alt="{{ block.settings.background_image.alt | escape }}"
        class="ai-premium-hero__background-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
        loading="eager"
        width="{{ block.settings.background_image.width }}"
        height="{{ block.settings.background_image.height }}"
      >
    {% else %}
      <div style="background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }}; width: 100%; height: 100%;"></div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if block.settings.enable_overlay %}
      <div class="ai-premium-hero__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="ai-premium-hero__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-premium-hero__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-premium-hero__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.badge_text != blank %}
          <span class="ai-premium-hero__badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.badge_text }}</span>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.product_image_1 or block.settings.product_image_2 or block.settings.product_image_3 %}
          <div class="ai-premium-hero__product-images-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.product_image_1 %}
              <div class="ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <img
                  src="{{ block.settings.product_image_1 | image_url: width: 320 }}"
                  alt="{{ block.settings.product_image_1.alt | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="160"
                  height="160"
                >
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.product_image_2 %}
              <div class="ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <img
                  src="{{ block.settings.product_image_2 | image_url: width: 320 }}"
                  alt="{{ block.settings.product_image_2.alt | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="160"
                  height="160"
                >
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.product_image_3 %}
              <div class="ai-premium-hero__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <img
                  src="{{ block.settings.product_image_3 | image_url: width: 320 }}"
                  alt="{{ block.settings.product_image_3.alt | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="160"
                  height="160"
                >
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h1 class="ai-premium-hero__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h1>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
          <div class="ai-premium-hero__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.description }}</div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.primary_button_label != blank or block.settings.secondary_button_label != blank %}
          <div class="ai-premium-hero__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.primary_button_label != blank %}
              <a
                href="{{ block.settings.primary_button_url }}"
                class="ai-premium-hero__button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ block.settings.primary_button_label }}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.secondary_button_label != blank %}
              <a
                href="{{ block.settings.secondary_button_url }}"
                class="ai-premium-hero__button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ block.settings.secondary_button_label }}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.support_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-premium-hero__support-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.support_text }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-premium-hero__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-premium-hero__slider-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.slide_image_1 %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="0">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.slide_image_1 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.slide_image_1.alt | escape }}"
                loading="eager"
                width="{{ block.settings.slide_image_1.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.slide_image_1.height }}"
              >
            </div>
          {% else %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="0">
              <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'lifestyle-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.slide_image_2 %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="1">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.slide_image_2 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.slide_image_2.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.slide_image_2.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.slide_image_2.height }}"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.slide_image_3 %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="2">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.slide_image_3 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.slide_image_3.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.slide_image_3.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.slide_image_3.height }}"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.slide_image_4 %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="3">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.slide_image_4 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.slide_image_4.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.slide_image_4.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.slide_image_4.height }}"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.slide_image_5 %}
            <div class="ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="4">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.slide_image_5 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.slide_image_5.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.slide_image_5.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.slide_image_5.height }}"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        {% assign slide_count = 0 %}
        {% if block.settings.slide_image_1 %}{% assign slide_count = slide_count | plus: 1 %}{% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.slide_image_2 %}{% assign slide_count = slide_count | plus: 1 %}{% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.slide_image_3 %}{% assign slide_count = slide_count | plus: 1 %}{% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.slide_image_4 %}{% assign slide_count = slide_count | plus: 1 %}{% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.slide_image_5 %}{% assign slide_count = slide_count | plus: 1 %}{% endif %}

        {% if slide_count > 1 %}
          <div class="ai-premium-hero__dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% for i in (1..slide_count) %}
              <button
                class="ai-premium-hero__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                data-dot-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}"
                aria-label="Go to slide {{ forloop.index }}"
              ></button>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% if block.settings.enable_divider and block.settings.divider_image %}
    <div class="ai-premium-hero__divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <img
        src="{{ block.settings.divider_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}"
        alt="Decorative divider"
        loading="lazy"
        width="{{ block.settings.divider_image.width }}"
        height="{{ block.settings.divider_image.height }}"
      >
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</premium-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class PremiumHero{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.currentSlide = 0;
        this.slides = [];
        this.dots = [];
        this.autoplayInterval = null;
        this.isPaused = false;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.slides = Array.from(this.querySelectorAll('.ai-premium-hero__slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));
        this.dots = Array.from(this.querySelectorAll('.ai-premium-hero__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));
        
        if (this.slides.length === 0) return;

        this.slides[0].classList.add('active');
        if (this.dots.length > 0) {
          this.dots[0].classList.add('active');
        }

        this.setupEventListeners();
        
        {% if block.settings.enable_autoplay %}
          this.startAutoplay();
        {% endif %}
      }

      setupEventListeners() {
        this.dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
          dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
            this.goToSlide(index);
          });
        });

        {% if block.settings.pause_on_hover %}
          const slider = this.querySelector('.ai-premium-hero__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          slider.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
            this.pauseAutoplay();
          });
          slider.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
            this.resumeAutoplay();
          });
        {% endif %}
      }

      goToSlide(index) {
        this.slides[this.currentSlide].classList.remove('active');
        if (this.dots.length > 0) {
          this.dots[this.currentSlide].classList.remove('active');
        }

        this.currentSlide = index;

        this.slides[this.currentSlide].classList.add('active');
        if (this.dots.length > 0) {
          this.dots[this.currentSlide].classList.add('active');
        }
      }

      nextSlide() {
        const nextIndex = (this.currentSlide + 1) % this.slides.length;
        this.goToSlide(nextIndex);
      }

      startAutoplay() {
        if (this.slides.length <= 1) return;
        
        this.autoplayInterval = setInterval(() => {
          if (!this.isPaused) {
            this.nextSlide();
          }
        }, {{ block.settings.autoplay_speed }});
      }

      pauseAutoplay() {
        this.isPaused = true;
      }

      resumeAutoplay() {
        this.isPaused = false;
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        if (this.autoplayInterval) {
          clearInterval(this.autoplayInterval);
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('premium-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}', PremiumHero{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Premium hero",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Background"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "background_image",
      "label": "Background image"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background color",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "enable_overlay",
      "label": "Enable dark overlay",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "overlay_color",
      "label": "Overlay color",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "overlay_opacity",
      "label": "Overlay opacity",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "%",
      "default": 50
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Badge"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
